CircleAvatar is a widget used to show a circular profile image, icon, or text.
You commonly use it for profile photos (like WhatsApp, Instagram).
CircleAvatar(
  radius: 40,
  backgroundColor: Colors.blue,
  child: Text("A"),
)

CircleAvatar(
  radius: 50,
  backgroundImage: AssetImage("assets/images/user.jpg"),
)

CircleAvatar(
  radius: 30,
  backgroundColor: Colors.green,
  child: Icon(Icons.person, size: 30, color: Colors.white),
)
